content.text: - Lily AI: Enterprise SaaS with custom pricing, "Request a Demo" model with no public pricing - ThredUp: Platform-integrated features freely available to all ThredUp users - Syte.ai: Enterprise SaaS with custom pricing, "Request a Demo" model with no public pricing - Donde Search: Enterprise SaaS with custom pricing (before acquisition by Shopify) - Ximilar: Tiered subscription with transparent pricing (Free: €0, Business 100K: €59/$64 monthly, Professional 1M: €499/$549 monthly)
